<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <meta charset="utf-8">
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: 'Arial', sans-serif;
            line-height: 1.6;
            color: #333;
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 20px;
        }
        .header {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #667eea 0%, #764ba2 100%);
            padding: 30px;
            text-align: center;
            border-radius: 10px 10px 0 0;
        }
        .header h1 {
            color: white;
            margin: 0;
            font-size: 24px;
        }
        .content {
            background: #f9f9f9;
            padding: 30px;
            border-radius: 0 0 10px 10px;
        }
        .otp-code {
            background: #667eea;
            color: white;
            padding: 15px 30px;
            font-size: 32px;
            font-weight: bold;
            text-align: center;
            border-radius: 5px;
            letter-spacing: 5px;
            margin: 20px 0;
        }
        .footer {
            text-align: center;
            margin-top: 30px;
            font-size: 12px;
            color: #666;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="header">
        <h1>Verify Your Account</h1>
    </div>
    <div class="content">
        <h2>Hello {{name}},</h2>
        <p>Thank you for registering with us! Use the OTP code below to verify your account:</p>
        
        <div class="otp-code">{{otp}}</div>
        
        <p>This OTP will expire in 10 minutes. If you didn't request this code, please ignore this email.</p>
        
        <p>Best regards,<br>Your App Team</p>
    </div>
    <div class="footer">
        <p>&copy; {{year}} Your Company Name. All rights reserved.</p>
    </div>
</body>
</html>